{"tid":522182,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有絕食抗議咁有冇暴食抗議","createTime":"2018-01-07T09:58:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-07T11:17:50.000Z","uid":109983,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"33963416bc674a9d250698a082f8e85f00e58346","tid":522182,"uid":109983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T09:58:08.000Z","msg":"各位cc台鍵青好<br />\n是咁的<br />\n留意到絕食抗爭似乎已經無效果 社會都無咩回饋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有絕食咁有冇暴食抗爭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n暴飲暴食食到當場窒息休克<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔死後續高血壓糖尿心臟病 令政府社會關注<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點睇 我係未好有腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da6cf86b368dd00457f375365df5c2b507e44099","tid":522182,"uid":36478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T10:02:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68e2fa9bc5e9a5b073761e2abd6857413c0f7ddf","tid":522182,"uid":109983,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T10:04:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n64 71 11籌款日賺唔少"},{"pid":"a51e1ae56f96400771c520419aaad50b0c674b6c","tid":522182,"uid":75326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"da6cf86b368dd00457f375365df5c2b507e44099","tid":522182,"uid":36478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T10:02:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T10:04:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcb15e0629010c6cece460088233df9f6f92ae12","tid":522182,"uid":109983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r